So, TECLOGI was born aiming to solve some of the several challenges we face in the supply chain in Latin America, like a challenging geography, security risks, several intermediaries, and huge security risks.

Operational versatility, which means that,

* A marketplace to connect cargo with safe vehicles

We are also going to set our HQ in Europe while maintaining our operation in Argentina primarily to continue to have the advantage of an exceptional tech team at a low cost. 

Our mission is to help companies improve the quality of their products and services by providing them with a platform that can be used for recruiting the best talent, increase the quality of workforce training, monitor and provide top support while reducing the effort and costs. We foresee that in the coming months we will enable our client’s teams to be present anywhere from the comfort of their homes or offices without traveling.

We help humans interact better with objects by combining XR with AI. At this moment we have two products:
* Website for monitoring industrial processes.

If AR is not enough then the user performs a call with a support team and receives 3D Gestures to fix it.  This is also used to train employees and to validate their knowledge on certain subjects.
* VR Remote support is coming soon.

Two CSR are being carried on, teaching people how to generate income by themselves in IT. Most of the attendants are either non-technical or vulnerable people. The other CSR is a AR app free for students at school so they can live the education and get better results.
